DYqL4B3kQ7kNvgG_baUY&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBzwqmj-G-RyIYqYxhEATKtNwLLvtlbDQunq2AjJ38NFA&oe=671B6962"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Sling TV", "keywords": ["TV", "sports", "shows", "television", "drama"], "long_description": "Sling TV is live TV, only better. The #1 live TV streaming service that lets you personalize your channel lineup and save. \n\nStart with the service best for you, then pick Extras in your favorite genres: Sports, Comedy, Kids, News, Movies, Lifestyle, Spanish, & more. Change your service online anytime.\n\nOver 100 live channels available to stream instantly on all of your favorite devices. Watch your favorite live sports like the NFL & college football, hit TV shows like Fear the Walking Dead, Better Call Saul, SportsCenter, plus 10,000+ hours of on-demand tv shows and movies.\n\nWith Sling TV you can get both TV and Cloud DVR on your terms - add it when you want and choose when you watch, for just $5\n\nThis is TV on your terms. No paying for useless channels, no long-term contracts, no hidden fees, easy online cancellation.\n\nThe Sling Orange service offers 30 channels for just $25/mo \u2013 including ESPN, Disney Channel, AMC, TNT, TBS, CNN, A&E, History, and many more.", "short_description": "Sling TV is live TV, only better. The #1 live TV streaming service that lets you personalize your channel lineup and save.\n\nStart with the service best for you, then pick Extras in your favorite genres: Sports, Comedy, Kids, News, Movies, Lifestyle, Spanish, & more. Change your service online anytime."}]}, "developer_name": "Sling TV, LLC", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.sling.com/offer-details/disclaimers/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.sling.com/offer-details/disclaimers/terms-of-use", "publisher_name": "Sling TV, LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.sling.com/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfor